data.title: German Command and Control KDE
data.text:
Hi

Here is my first submission to control the KDE Desktop a bit better with your German voice. :-D

For now there are only the most used programs as you can see.

Also it is only the names of the programms, so you can start them etc.

My plan is to make more recordings with the most used commands from these programms, like next song, open file etc.

While this will not in all programms be enough to only use your voice to control them, it certainly is a start

As of now (28/03/2014) none of these words is in ther german speech model.

####

With this you can control mypaint to like 90 % also basic control of a webbrowser, amarok, clementine, and movie player. Also many more it just depends how you use them.

Have fun :-D

Here we go again, this time this nearly completes all the use cases I can think of. This is more for a general apprach like reboot the pc with your voice and control Webcam and post the picture of facebook or twitter.

For now, consider this the last sumission for me. I really cant think of more use cases for now. However if they pop into my mind i will post another one, or if someone else has a idea.

These words are also not in the German model from guenter.

cya soon
